Type: Package
Package: blorr
Title: Tools for Developing Binary Logistic Regression Models
Version: 0.0.9
Authors@R: person("Aravind", "Hebbali", email = "hebbali.aravind@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for developing and monitoring binary logistic regression 
    models. Includes comprehensive regression output, variable selection 
    procedure and model validation statistics.
